♫Silver candles light up in the autumn♫

169
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:38,330
[Pavilion of Pleasantness]

170
00:13:33,730 --> 00:13:45,020
♫Cold painted screen♫

171
00:13:49,260 --> 00:14:00,840
♫The blue sky is like water and the night clouds♫

